#: ../../B/bit-twiddling.rst:5
msgid "bit twiddling"
msgstr "bit twiddling"

#: ../../B/bit-twiddling.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../B/bit-twiddling.rst:9
msgid "[very common]"
msgstr "[非常に一般的]"

#: ../../B/bit-twiddling.rst:12
msgid ""
"(pejorative) An exercise in tuning (see :ref:`tune`\\) in which incredible "
"amounts of time and effort go to produce little noticeable improvement, "
"often with the result that the code becomes incomprehensible."
msgstr ""
"(侮蔑的)信じがたいほどの時間と労力をかけて、ほとんど目立った改善を生まないチューニング(\\ :ref:`tune`\\ "
"を参照)の作業で、しばしばコードが理解不能になるという結果に終わる。"

#: ../../B/bit-twiddling.rst:15
msgid "Aimless small modification to a program, esp. for some pointless goal."
msgstr "プログラムへの、特に無意味な目標のための、当てのない小さな変更。"

#: ../../B/bit-twiddling.rst:19
msgid ""
"Approx. syn. for :ref:`bit-bashing`\\; esp. used for the act of frobbing the"
" device control register of a peripheral in an attempt to get it back to a "
"known state."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`bit-bashing`\\ のほぼ同義語。特に、周辺機器のデバイス制御レジスタをfrobして既知の状態に戻そうとする行為に使う。"
